04. RFC 3875 is available at http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3875 <dt id="refsUNICODE"> [UNICODE] <dd> <cite> <a href="http://www.unicode.org/versions/Unicode4.0.0/"> The Unicode Standard, Version 4.0 </a> </cite> , The Unicode Consortium. Boston, MA, Addison-Wesley, 2003. ISBN 0-321-18578-1. The latest version of the Unicode specification is available at <a
